    public class HomeFragment
extends com.actionbarsherlock.app.SherlockFragment
implements android.view.View.OnClickListener
    This class holds the HomeFragment which is nested in the MainMenuActivity. It displays rank, name, available points, progress and an avatar.
    Author:
    Dimitri Mantler
